tles\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also a welcome respite from the scorching heat enveloping the city this week.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a welcome respite\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"the scorching heat\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians and tourists alike, looking to cool off this summer, can dive in - weather permitting - at three bathing sites: one close to Paris's Notre-Dame cathedral, another near the Eiffel Tower and a third in eastern Paris.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.52006673302638e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.52006673302638e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"weather\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"three bathing sites\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming zones are equipped with changing rooms, showers and beach-style furniture, offering space for 150 to 300 swimmers.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The swimming zones\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"changing rooms\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"showers\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\